{"desi_lesson":{"title":"Days of the Week","target_language":"Kannada","theme":"Days of the Week","vocabulary":[{"english":"Sunday","target_language_script":"ಭಾನುವಾರ","transliteration":"bhaanuvaara","pronunciation":"bha-noo-vah-rah"},{"english":"Monday","target_language_script":"ಸೋಮವಾರ","transliteration":"som avaara","pronunciation":"so-mah-vah-rah"},{"english":"Tuesday","target_language_script":"ಮಂಗಳವಾರ","transliteration":"mangaLavaara","pronunciation":"mang-ga-lah-vah-rah"},{"english":"Wednesday","target_language_script":"ಬುಧವಾರ","transliteration":"budhavaara","pronunciation":"bud-ha-vah-rah"},{"english":"Thursday","target_language_script":"ಗುರುವಾರ","transliteration":"guruvaara","pronunciation":"gu-roo-vah-rah"},{"english":"Friday","target_language_script":"ಶುಕ್ರವಾರ","transliteration":"shukravaara","pronunciation":"shu-kra-vah-rah"},{"english":"Saturday","target_language_script":"ಶನಿವಾರ","transliteration":"shanivaara","pronunciation":"sha-nee-vah-rah"},{"english":"day","target_language_script":"ದಿನ","transliteration":"dina","pronunciation":"dee-nah"},{"english":"week","target_language_script":"ವಾರ","transliteration":"vaara","pronunciation":"vah-rah"},{"english":"today","target_language_script":"ಇಂದು","transliteration":"indu","pronunciation":"in-doo"}],"example_sentences":[{"english":"Today is Monday.","target_language_script":"ಇಂದು ಸೋಮವಾರ.","transliteration":"indu somavaara.","pronunciation":"in-doo so-mah-vah-rah."},{"english":"Tomorrow is Tuesday.","target_language_script":"ನಾಳೆ ಮಂಗಳವಾರ.","transliteration":"naale mangaLavaara.","pronunciation":"nah-leh mang-ga-lah-vah-rah."},{"english":"What day is it today?","target_language_script":"ಇಂದು ಯಾವ ದಿನ?","transliteration":"indu yaava dina?","pronunciation":"in-doo yah-vah dee-nah?"},{"english":"It is Sunday.","target_language_script":"ಇದು ಭಾನುವಾರ.","transliteration":"idu bhaanuvaara.","pronunciation":"ee-doo bha-noo-vah-rah."},{"english":"My favorite day is Friday.","target_language_script":"ನನ್ನ ಪ್ರೀತಿಯ ದಿನ ಶುಕ್ರವಾರ.","transliteration":"nanna Preetiya dina shukravaara.","pronunciation":"nan-na pree-tee-yah dee-nah shu-kra-vah-rah."}],"short_story":{"title":"Planning the Week","dialogue":[{"speaker":"Person A","target_language_script":"ಇಂದು ಭಾನುವಾರ, ನಾಳೆ ಸೋಮವಾರ.","transliteration":"indu bhaanuvaara, naale somavaara.","english":"Today is Sunday, tomorrow is Monday."},{"speaker":"Person B","target_language_script":"ಹೌದು, ಸೋಮವಾರ ನನಗೆ ಕೆಲಸ ಇದೆ.","transliteration":"haadu, somavaara nanage kelasa ide.","english":"Yes, I have work on Monday."}]},"quiz":[{"question":"How do you say 'Monday' in Kannada?","options":["bhaanuvaara","som avaara","mangaLavaara","budhavaara"],"answer":"som avaara"},{"question":"What is the Kannada word for 'day'?","options":["vaara","dina","indu","naale"],"answer":"dina"},{"question":"How do you say 'Friday' in Kannada?","options":["guruvaara","shanivaara","shukravaara","som avaara"],"answer":"shukravaara"},{"question":"What is the Kannada word for 'today'?","options":["naale","indu","addu","idu"],"answer":"indu"}]}}